    "minides": "The design-led Range Rover, sitting between Evoque and Range Rover Sport — minimalist styling, flush door handles, and a reductive cabin.",
    "description": "The Range Rover Velar is Land Rover's design-focused mid-size luxury SUV, positioned between the Evoque and Range Rover Sport. Known for its clean surfacing, hidden door handles, and uncluttered dual-touchscreen cabin, it is sold in India in a single fully-loaded Autobiography trim, offered with a choice of 2.0L turbo-petrol or 2.0L turbo-diesel Ingenium engines, both paired with an 8-speed automatic and full-time AWD. Standard equipment includes electronic air suspension, Terrain Response 2, a 11.4-inch Pivi Pro touchscreen, Meridian sound system, and a comprehensive ADAS-light safety suite."
  },
